      "gridPos": { "h": 3, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 2 },
      "options": { "mode": "markdown", "content": "# AEGIS Forecast Drift — Historical Timeline\n\nChronological governed view of forecast versions and detected drift — **V2** snapshot (read-only). Each timeline record is a governed drift event positioned by its **forecast_version**. Use the **Date Range** and shared filters above." }
